.git
.github
.agents
.codex
target
**/target
dist
**/node_modules

# 真实配置、凭据和运行产物不能进入构建上下文或镜像层。
.env
**/.env
!runtime/config/.env.example
**/*.key
**/*.pem
runtime/config/secrets
runtime/config/runtime.toml
runtime/config/ops.toml
runtime/data
runtime/logs
runtime/run
runtime/media
runtime/qq-maid-bot
runtime/*.sh
runtime/*.cmd
runtime/*.ps1

# 私有 Prompt / 知识资料默认忽略，仅保留公开 example 模板。
runtime/config/prompts/*.md
!runtime/config/prompts/*.example.md
runtime/config/knowledge/**/*.md
runtime/config/knowledge/**/*.markdown
!runtime/config/knowledge/**/*.example.md
!runtime/config/knowledge/**/*.example.markdown

scripts/deploy.conf
*.log
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
